### AI SaaS Backend API Examples
### Use with REST Client extensions like VS Code REST Client

# Set base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### 1. Generate Simple Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/content/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "type": "content",
  "prompt": "Write a professional email announcing a new product launch",
  "config": {
    "maxTokens": 500,
    "temperature": 0.7
  }
}

### 2. Generate YouTube Script
POST {{baseUrl}}/content/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "type": "youtube_script",
  "prompt": "The Future of Artificial Intelligence",
  "config": {
    "duration": "10 minutes",
    "style": "educational",
    "maxTokens": 1500
  }
}

### 3. Generate SEO Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/content/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "type": "seo_content",
  "prompt": "Artificial intelligence is transforming how businesses operate in the digital age.",
  "keywords": ["AI", "business transformation", "digital age", "automation"],
  "config": {
    "maxTokens": 1000,
    "temperature": 0.5
  }
}

### 4. Create Simple Content Generation Workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Blog Post Generator",
  "description": "Generates blog posts using AI",
  "type": "content_generation",
  "userId": "user123",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "generate-content",
      "name": "Generate Blog Content",
      "type": "ai_generation",
      "config": {
        "generationType": "content",
        "prompt": "Write a comprehensive blog post about the benefits of AI automation for small businesses",
        "maxTokens": 1500,
        "temperature": 0.7
      },
      "order": 0
    }
  ]
}

### 5. Create Multi-Step YouTube Workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "YouTube Content Pipeline",
  "description": "Complete YouTube video creation pipeline",
  "type": "youtube_script",
  "userId": "user123",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "script-generation",
      "name": "Generate YouTube Script",
      "type": "ai_generation",
      "config": {
        "generationType": "youtube_script",
        "prompt": "10 Ways AI Can Boost Your Productivity",
        "duration": "12 minutes",
        "style": "educational",
        "maxTokens": 2000
      },
      "order": 0
    }
  ]
}

### 6. Create SEO Optimization Workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "SEO Content Optimizer",
  "description": "Optimizes content for search engines",
  "type": "seo_writing",
  "userId": "user123",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "seo-optimization",
      "name": "Optimize for SEO",
      "type": "ai_generation",
      "config": {
        "generationType": "seo_content",
        "prompt": "Our new AI-powered analytics platform provides real-time insights and predictive modeling for businesses of all sizes.",
        "keywords": ["AI analytics", "real-time insights", "predictive modeling", "business intelligence"],
        "maxTokens": 2000
      },
      "order": 0
    }
  ]
}

### 7. Execute Workflow (Replace WORKFLOW_ID with actual ID from previous responses)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/WORKFLOW_ID/execute
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "input": {
    "targetAudience": "small business owners",
    "tone": "professional"
  }
}

### 8. Check Workflow Execution Status (Replace EXECUTION_ID with actual ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/executions/EXECUTION_ID/status

### 9. Create Complex Automation Pipeline
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Content Marketing Pipeline",
  "description": "Complete content marketing automation",
  "type": "automation_pipeline",
  "userId": "user123",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "research",
      "name": "Topic Research",
      "type": "ai_generation",
      "config": {
        "generationType": "content",
        "prompt": "Research trending topics in AI and automation for Q4 2024",
        "maxTokens": 800
      },
      "order": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "blog-post",
      "name": "Generate Blog Post",
      "type": "ai_generation",
      "config": {
        "generationType": "content",
        "prompt": "Write a detailed blog post based on the research findings",
        "maxTokens": 2000
      },
      "order": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "social-media",
      "name": "Create Social Media Content",
      "type": "ai_generation",
      "config": {
        "generationType": "content",
        "prompt": "Create 5 social media posts promoting the blog post",
        "maxTokens": 600
      },
      "order": 2
    }
  ]
}

### 10. Error Handling Example - Invalid Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/content/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "type": "invalid_type",
  "prompt": ""
}

### 11. Rate Limiting Test (Send multiple requests quickly)
POST {{baseUrl}}/content/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "type": "content",
  "prompt": "Quick test message",
  "config": {
    "maxTokens": 100
  }
}
